com.vaadin.polymer.neon

Interface SlideFromTopAnimationElement

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Element, EventTarget, HTMLElement, Node

    @JsType(isNative=true)
public interface SlideFromTopAnimationElement
extends HTMLElement

    <slide-from-top-animation> animates the transform of an element from translateY(-100%) to
    none. The transformOrigin defaults to 50% 0.

    Configuration:

    {
   name: 'slide-from-top-animation',
   node: <node>,
   transformOrigin: <transform-origin>,
   timing: <animation-timing>
 }
